text.tspan: When our Founder moved to Austin from Pennsylvania in 1980,
he brought with him a desire to serve great food in a place
where everyone was treated like family. When he started serving
Philly’s favorite sandwich with a Texas twist – he realized he had
captured the perfect blend of Texas and Philadelphia – and by
combining the two, a Legend was born. We’ve opened a few
more restaurants and added some great new items to the menu
since then, but we’ve never wavered from the passion, quality
and commitment to a truly unique experience that has been a
part of Texadelphia from day one. We hope you enjoy!
